creator: Michele Lynch
title: Twin Flame Transformation - Obsession with your Twin Flame
dc:creator: Michele Lynch
content:
Episode 2:  In this episode, Michele dives into Twin Flame obsession and addiction. She shares how important it is to be conscious of the thoughts you have around your twin flame and stop the obsession and addiction before they become an unconscious behavior that controls you.
